<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Succour2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Succour,</orth> vb. (used only in the inf. pres.). to relieve, to help, to assist: <cit><quote>shine sun to s. flowers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 208" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 208</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>God will s. us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 4, 55</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 41</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.7.56" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 80</bibl>.
